  "aboutMe": {
    "content": "Hi, my name is Mady, I'm 23 years old and Im a hot 🔥 colombian 🇨🇴 girl! I just arrived Madrid and I love this city! 🏠 I live in a very nice house in Tres Cantos, close to Plaza Castilla. I offer great and relaxing massages! 💫 I live with a friend and we do a four hand massage that will make you go crazy so don't think more about it and contact me for more info, you can call me or better, text me by WhatsApp or Telegram! ☎️<br />\nSee you soon 💋",
